missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-008/refined/chain-03.md:5:This branch is live only if an exact stochastic transport or martingale representation yields more than probabilistic repackaging. Before investing in Tao-comparison or broad endpoint narratives, the chain must identify one candidate observable that is tied to a named blowup mechanism and has at least one of the following:
missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-008/refined/chain-03.md:8:- local or pathwise consequence, not only expectation-level content;
missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-008/refined/chain-03.md:9:- stability under the localization and stopping procedures required near singular behavior;
missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-008/refined/chain-03.md:12:If no such observable survives, the correct output is an obstruction memo saying that the stochastic structure is exact but theorem-irrelevant for the intended endpoint.
missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-008/refined/chain-03.md:18:- one conditional proposition linking a specific stochastic circulation, Cauchy-type transport quantity, backward-flow observable, or martingale to one named concentration, stretching, or continuation bottleneck; or
missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-008/refined/chain-03.md:19:- one calibrated obstruction memo showing failure by non-coercivity, expectation-only gain, solution-class mismatch, localization collapse, prior-art redundancy, parasitic framework import, Tao-insensitive packaging, or a stacked combination.
missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-008/refined/chain-03.md:23:This route still mines genuinely viscous-Lagrangian structure rather than standard Eulerian estimate chains. The difference is methodological: it no longer treats representational novelty as progress. A stochastic observable is promoted only if it touches a specific singularity mechanism under honest localization and regularity pressure.
